Overview:
Blueprint’s AI Notetaker listens, transcribes, and writes automated notes for thousands of mental health clinicians every week. With the Blueprint Chrome Extension, now you can use the full version of AI Notetaker without leaving your EHR! Whether your session is in-person or through any telehealth solution (EHR or standalone), you simply start recording, click ‘finish session’ and your automated notes will show up in the browser extension in record time. 

What makes the Blueprint Browser Extension unique? 
Suggest improvements and regenerate any note directly from the extension!
Review the progress note, session summary, transcript and more side by side before copying any of it over to your EHR.
Easily delete the notes from Blueprint the moment you transfer to your EHR
Output SOAP, DAP, BIRP, GIRP, EMDR and many other note types in the extension.
Copy/paste options: Copy and Paste either full notes or each note section to your EHR 
Instant installation and set up. Simply log in and start!

Free Trial & Pricing:
A free trial is available to everyone, and with no tiered plans, the Blueprint Chrome Extension is included for everyone!  It takes less than 2 minutes to get started. To jump in, start here: https://www.blueprint.ai.

About Blueprint:
Blueprint is the world’s first AI-powered assistant for therapists. With Blueprint, therapists can automate progress notes, draft smart treatment plans, and receive actionable insights before, during, and after every client session. To learn more, visit https://www.blueprint.ai
